Del can delete file and folder,but not remove,del move file and folder to a folder which you name it as trash.

How to use
$del filename  
You will move filename to a trash like /home/tmp.

=====>2011-6-24<=====
del-0.1
Move file and folder,but only one once a time.

=====>2011-7-2<=====
del-0.2
Move more files and folders.
Judge the same name file or folder in /home/tmp.

del-0.3
Use a log file to record the files and folders which be moved to tmp.
In the same way,use the log file to remove the file in cycle.
That's great and I like that.
